title: Kayu Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Organic, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Beachfront Cafe specializes in organic international cuisine. Offers cold pressed juices, smoothies, breakfast all day, paninis, desserts and more. Vegan choices are not labeled so please read ingredients listed on menu for each item and confirm with wait staff. English is spoken. Also sells local and international specialty organic items such as coconut syrups, teas, granola, energy bars, body care products, and more. Wi-fi access. Gets really busy at times.
